source.name: Chicago Public Schools - School Locations
source.description: Locations of each school in the Chicago Public Schools district. To view or use these shapefiles, compression software, such as 7-Zip, and special GIS software, such as ESRI ArcGIS or QGIS, are required. To download this file, right-click the "Download" link above and choose "Save link as."
